      "source_index": 1,
      "target_index": 3,
      "evolution_type": "semantic_extension",
      "note": "‘消除’、‘消灭’再引申为减少、损耗或退减物质。"
    },
    {
      "source_index": 1,
      "target_index": 4,
      "evolution_type": "semantic_shift",
      "note": "‘消’义在“不消说”中转为‘需要’，从‘耗’、‘损’之意广义引申。"
    },
    {
      "source_index": 1,
      "target_index": 5,
      "evolution_type": "semantic_extension",
      "note": "‘消’用于病名，因‘消耗’体内物质、衰减而得名。"
